data.description: This property has had SO many updates, all you need to do is  move in and enjoy! NEW Roof, HVAC, and garage doors 2021! NEW  siding 2022, along with a NEW and extended wooden privacy fence! Garage features a newly installed door to the side yard, accessing an extended patio, as well as an EV charging station. Inside find a wide open main level perfect for entertaining! Large family room is accentuated by recessed lighting and windows full of sunlight. Kitchen has NEW appliances, and is open to dining room and family room, and includes a large  island with breakfast bar for additional seating. Kitchen, Hall bath, and Owners bath updated beautifully in 2015.  NEW Flooring in bedrooms and basement 2022. Finished basement with bedroom and full bath. NEW Washer and Dryer 2022. NEW hot water heater 2023! Out back, find a lovely screened in deck with composite decking for low maintenance. Yard is situated on a corner lot for plenty of play space. NEW and oversized driveway provides plenty of parking!!
